ğŸ—ï¸ Project Structure (Clean Architecture)
/internal
   /config
   /domain
      /product
      /auth
      /order
      /payment
   /repository
   /service
   /transport
      /http (Echo handlers)
   /utils


This structure ensures:

High scalability

Loose coupling

Easy testing

Independent domain modules

